74
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,360
Mr. Gu.

75
00:07:52,070 --> 00:07:52,920
Have you located her?

76
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,870
We've spotted her potential traces,

77
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,750
